ActDepartment of Employment and Social Development Act
PrecisDesignation of PIERRE LALIBERTÉ of Gatineau Quebec, to act as commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission representing workers, to fill a vacancy in that office for a term of one year or until a commissioner is appointed, whichever is earlier, effective October 3, 2016.
